## 4. Naming conventions

| Thing | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Files (components) | PascalCase | `YarnCard.tsx` |
| Files (hooks, lib) | camelCase | `useStash.ts` |
| Files (screens) | kebab-case | `ravelry-import.tsx` |
| Components | PascalCase | `YarnCard` |
| Hooks | camelCase, prefix `use` | `useStash` |
| Types/interfaces | PascalCase, no `I` prefix | `YarnEntry`, `Project` |
| Supabase table rows | snake_case (matches DB) | `yarn_stash`, `current_weight_g` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE | `SUPABASE_URL` |
| CSS/NativeWind | Tailwind utility classes only | No inline StyleSheet |

